&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608060954.png&#34;
	width=&#34;320&#34;
	height=&#34;103&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608060954_hu_f9610dd76a11c9c3.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608060954_hu_9df6018f4a4accbf.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;310&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;745px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这里是输入IP地址的，填写你购买服务器的IP即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061029.png&#34;
	width=&#34;310&#34;
	height=&#34;200&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061029_hu_35efe8502997e1aa.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061029_hu_7db187ca7d68daa5.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;155&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;372px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这里是填写服务器端口与用户名密码的，如果你没有修改端口，则默认端口为22，用户名为root。
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061121.png&#34;
	width=&#34;237&#34;
	height=&#34;40&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061121_hu_8e0543315383f4da.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061121_hu_f5c5fa0bb84a20ee.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;592&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1422px&#34;
	
&gt; &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061128.png&#34;
	width=&#34;272&#34;
	height=&#34;207&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061128_hu_472119881bb140ad.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061128_hu_8d8a49dcebff9f68.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;131&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;315px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;点击添加密码，输入你的密码即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;添加完你就可以在主页看到你添加的服务器了，双击连接即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如果连接失败，请查看服务器防火墙与账号密码是否正确。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;检查防火墙&#34;&gt;检查防火墙
&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061704.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1577&#34;
	height=&#34;359&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061704_hu_c81e78cf83c39122.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/post/2024060801/updata20240608061704_hu_50f30f0748f681dd.png 1024w&#34;
